#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.105"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.105:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.105:0.2"
msgid "11. Valāhakavagga"
msgstr "11. Clouds"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.105:0.3"
msgid "105. Ambasutta"
msgstr "105. Mangoes"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.105:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, ambāni."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four mangoes."

msgctxt "an4.105:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri?"
msgstr "What four?"

#. VAR: pakkavaṇṇi → pakkavaṇṇī (bj, s2, s3, km)
#. VAR: āmavaṇṇi → āmavaṇṇī (bj, s2, s3, km)
#. VAR: āmavaṇṇi → āmavaṇṇī (bj, s2, s3, km)
#. VAR: pakkavaṇṇi → pakkavaṇṇī (bj, s2, s3, km)
msgctxt "an4.105:1.3"
msgid "Āmaṃ pakkavaṇṇi, pakkaṃ āmavaṇṇi, āmaṃ āmavaṇṇi, pakkaṃ pakkavaṇṇi—"
msgstr ""
"~One is unripe but seems ripe, ~one is ripe but seems unripe, ~one is unripe "
"and seems unripe, and ~one is ripe and seems ripe."

msgctxt "an4.105:1.4"
msgid "imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri ambāni."
msgstr "These are the four mangoes."

#. VAR: cattāro → cattāro’me (bj, s1-3, km)
msgctxt "an4.105:1.5"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, cattāro ambūpamā puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā "
"lokasmiṃ."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, these four people similar to mangoes are found in the world."

msgctxt "an4.105:1.6"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.105:1.7"
msgid "Āmo pakkavaṇṇī, pakko āmavaṇṇī, āmo āmavaṇṇī, pakko pakkavaṇṇī."
msgstr ""
"~One is unripe but seems ripe, ~one is ripe but seems unripe, ~one is unripe "
"and seems unripe, and ~one is ripe and seems ripe."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.107"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.105:2.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo āmo hoti pakkavaṇṇī?"
msgstr "And how is a person unripe but seems ripe?"

msgctxt "an4.105:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekaccassa puggalassa pāsādikaṃ hoti abhikkantaṃ paṭikkantaṃ "
"ālokitaṃ vilokitaṃ samiñjitaṃ pasāritaṃ saṅghāṭipattacīvaradhāraṇaṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a person is impressive when going out and coming back, when "
"looking ahead and aside, when bending and extending the limbs, and when "
"bearing the outer robe, bowl and robes."

msgctxt "an4.105:2.3"
msgid ""
"So ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī "
"paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti."
msgstr ""
"But they don’t really understand: ‘This is suffering’ … ‘This is the origin "
"of suffering’ … ‘This is the cessation of suffering’ … ‘This is the practice "
"that leads to the cessation of suffering’."

msgctxt "an4.105:2.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo āmo hoti pakkavaṇṇī."
msgstr "That’s how a person is unripe but seems ripe."

msgctxt "an4.105:2.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi taṃ, bhikkhave, ambaṃ āmaṃ pakkavaṇṇi;"
msgstr "That person is like a mango that’s unripe but seems ripe, I say."

msgctxt "an4.105:2.6"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.105:3.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo pakko hoti āmavaṇṇī?"
msgstr "And how is a person ripe but seems unripe?"

msgctxt "an4.105:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekaccassa puggalassa na pāsādikaṃ hoti abhikkantaṃ "
"paṭikkantaṃ ālokitaṃ vilokitaṃ samiñjitaṃ pasāritaṃ "
"saṅghāṭipattacīvaradhāraṇaṃ."
msgstr "It’s when a person is not impressive …"

msgctxt "an4.105:3.3"
msgid ""
"So ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī "
"paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr "But they really understand: ‘This is suffering’ …"

msgctxt "an4.105:3.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo pakko hoti āmavaṇṇī."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.105:3.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi taṃ, bhikkhave, ambaṃ pakkaṃ āmavaṇṇi;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.105:3.6"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.105:4.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo āmo hoti āmavaṇṇī?"
msgstr "And how is a person unripe and seems unripe?"

msgctxt "an4.105:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekaccassa puggalassa na pāsādikaṃ hoti abhikkantaṃ "
"paṭikkantaṃ ālokitaṃ vilokitaṃ samiñjitaṃ pasāritaṃ "
"saṅghāṭipattacīvaradhāraṇaṃ."
msgstr "It’s when a person is not impressive …"

msgctxt "an4.105:4.3"
msgid ""
"So ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī "
"paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti."
msgstr "Nor do they really understand: ‘This is suffering’ …"

msgctxt "an4.105:4.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo āmo hoti āmavaṇṇī."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.105:4.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi taṃ, bhikkhave, ambaṃ āmaṃ āmavaṇṇi;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.105:4.6"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.105:5.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo pakko hoti pakkavaṇṇī?"
msgstr "And how is a person ripe and seems ripe?"

msgctxt "an4.105:5.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekaccassa puggalassa pāsādikaṃ hoti abhikkantaṃ paṭikkantaṃ "
"ālokitaṃ vilokitaṃ samiñjitaṃ pasāritaṃ saṅghāṭipattacīvaradhāraṇaṃ."
msgstr "It’s when a person is impressive …"

msgctxt "an4.105:5.3"
msgid ""
"So ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī "
"paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr "And they really understand: ‘This is suffering’ …"

msgctxt "an4.105:5.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo pakko hoti pakkavaṇṇī."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.105:5.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi taṃ, bhikkhave, ambaṃ pakkaṃ pakkavaṇṇi;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.105:5.6"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.105:5.7"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro ambūpamā puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmin”ti."
msgstr "These four people similar to mangoes are found in the world.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.105:5.8"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
